Refer: https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E19253-01/819-5461/gaynp/index.html

REMOVE:
zpool remove <pool-name> <device> # note, no need to give details like mirror, cache etc.
example: zpool remove gitlab sdi

ADD
zpool add <pool-name> <sub-classification> <device> # sub-classification would be mirror, cache etc, etc.
example: zpool add gitlab mirror sdi
